name: campaign_id
description: Campaign ID

name: campaign_name
description: Campaign Name

name: adgroup_id
description: Ad group ID

name: adgroup_name
description: Ad group Name

name: ad_id
description: Ad ID

name: ad_name
description: Ad Name

name: tracking_pixel_id
description: The pixel ID that you'd like to track. You can use this field to track offsite events that do not happen on the TikTok instant page.

name: identity_id
description: Identity ID, required when you use Spark Ads (tiktok_item_id). If you are not using Spark Ads, we still highly recommend you to pass in ideneity_id and identity_type (CUSTOMIZED_USER) for better management of ads information.

name: identity_type
description: Identity type. Enum: CUSTOMIZED_USER, AUTH_CODE, TT_USER, BC_AUTH_TT.

name: identity_authorized_bc_id
description: Identity ID of a TikTok account that a Business Center is authorized to access. Required when identity_type is BC_AUTH_TT.

name: call_to_action
description: For call-to-action text, see Enumeration - Call-to-action

name: call_to_action_id
description: The ID of the CTA portfolio that you want to use in your ads. A CTA portfolio is a group of auto-optimized CTAs. If both this field and call_to_action are specified, call_to_action will be ignored. For details about dynamic CTAs, see CTA Recommendations - Dynamic CTAs.

name: card_id
description: Image card ID, gift code card ID, premium badge ID, Countdown Sticker ID, or Download Card ID.

name: secondary_status
description: Ad status（Secondary status，See Enumeration - Secondary Status

name: operation_status
description: Operation status, optional values include: DISABLE (the ad is disabled), ENABLE (the ad is enabled), FROZEN (the ad is terminated and cannot be enabled)

name: is_aco
description: Whether the ad is an automated ad. Set to true for automated ad and false for non-automated ad

name: image_ids
description: A list of image IDs

name: ad_format
description: The creative type. Enum values: SINGLE_IMAGE, SINGLE_VIDEO, CAROUSEL.

name: ad_text
description: The ad text. It is shown to your audience as part of your ad creative, to deliver the message you intend to communicate to them. Keyword match type is exact match.

name: ad_texts
description: A list of ad texts.

name: video_id
description: The video ID. When TikTok posts are used as ads, video_id is invalid. You can get the the ID of a TikTok post via the tiktok_item_id field.

name: tiktok_item_id
description: The ID of the TikTok post to be used as an ad. It can be obtained from Get Spark Ad post endpoint.

name: app_name
description: App name that is displayed in the ad.

name: landing_page_url
description: Landing page URL

name: landing_page_urls
description: Multiple landing page URLs

name: display_name
description: The display name of landing page or pure exposure ad

name: profile_image_url
description: Avatar URL

name: impression_tracking_url
description: Display monitoring URL

name: click_tracking_url
description: Click monitoring URL.

name: deeplink
description: The specific location where you want your audience to go if they have your app installed. See deeplink_type for more.

name: deeplink_type
description: The open URL type. Allowed values differs based on campaign objectives. Allowed values: NORMAL(supported in Traffic, Conversion & CatalogSales), DEFERRED_DEEPLINK(supported in AppInstall & Catalog Sales).

name: fallback_type
description: Fallback Type. If the audience do not have the app installed, you can have them fall back to install the app, or to view a specific web page. Not applicable for Deferred Deeplink. Enum values: APP_INSTALL, WEBSITE, UNSET. If website is chosen, you need to specify the url via landing_page_url field.

name: playable_url
description: Playable material url

name: page_id
description: Instant Page (Instant Form, storefront page, tiktok instant page or app profile page) ID

name: vast_moat_enabled
description: Whether Moat Viewability Verification is enabled for the ad. TikTok has partnered with Moat to launch viewability measurement for Brand Auction and Reach & Frequency In-feed ads purchased on TikTok for Business.

name: creative_authorized
description: Whether you grant displaying some of your ads in our TikTok For Business Creative Center. Only valid for non-US advertisers, the default value is false. Note: creative_authorized can only be used for video ads.

name: is_new_structure
description: Whether the campaign is a new structure (for the same campaign, the structure of campaign, adgroups and ads are the same)

name: create_time
description: Time at which the ad was created.

name: modify_time
description: Time at which the ad was modified.

name: shopping_ads_fallback_type
description: In shopping ads scenario, the fallback behavior of deeplink evokes failed. This field is returned when the corresponding campaign objective_type is CATALOG_SALES/PRODUCT_SALES. Enum values: DEFAULT(Application Installation), CUSTOM(Custom Landing Page), SHOPPING_ADS(Catalog Product Link)

name: shopping_ads__deeplink_type
description: Indicates the source of the direct link used in the ad. This field is returned when the corresponding campaign objective_type is CATALOG_SALES/PRODUCT_SALES. Enum values: NONE(not enabled), CUSTOM(custom direct link), SHOPPING_ADS(commodity direct link). The default value is NONE

name: shopping_ads_video_package_id
description: Catalog video template ID. Return when the corresponding campaign objective_type is CATALOG_SALES/PRODUCT_SALES.

name: promotional_music_disabled
description: Whether to disable the promotional use of the music in the Spark Ad post. The default value is true. If you want to allow dueting and stitching for the Spark Ad post, you need to set this field to false. This field is only valid for Spark Ad posts.

name: dark_post_status
description: Indicates whether the ad is a Spark Ads dark post. Enum value: ON, OFF.

name: branded_content_disabled
description: Default is false. If branded_content_disabled is true, you cannot modify dark_post_status.

name: item_duet_status
description: Whether to enable dueting for the Spark Ad post. This field is valid only when promotional_music_disabled is set to false. Enum values: ENABLE, DISABLE. This field is only valid for Spark Ad posts.

name: item_stitch_status
description: Whether to enable stitching for the Spark Ad post. This field is valid only when promotional_music_disabled is set to false. Enum values: ENABLE, DISABLE. This field is only valid for Spark Ad posts.

name: brand_safety_postbid_partner
description: Brand safety post bid measurement partner. Enumerations: Zefr.

name: product_specific_type
description: Different dimensions to choose products. Enum values: ALL, PRODUCT_SET, CUSTOMIZED_PRODUCTS.If you choose ALL, you don't need to input sku_ids or item_group_ids or product_set_id. item_group_ids or product_set_id are required if product_specific_type=PRODUCT_SET. sku_ids are required if product_specific_type=CUSTOMIZED_PRODUCTS

name: catalog_id
description: The catalog you choose for your ads.

name: item_group_ids
description: Product SPU ID.

name: product_set_id
description: The ID of the product set.

name: sku_ids
description: IDs of the SKUs

name: dynamic_format
description: Enum values: UNSET, DYNAMIC_CREATIVE(smart creative).

name: vertical_video_strategy
description: Enum values: UNSET, CUSTOM(single video), TPL_VIDEO(catalog videos), LIVE_STREAM . It must be UNSET if dynamic_format = DYNAMIC_CREATIVE.

name: dynamic_destination
description: Enum values: UNSET, DLP(Dynamic Landing Page)
